              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "I'm also planning on running free online seminars for members only, addressing single relevant issues in detail. These will be available afterwards as both videos and written articles. The frequency will depend a lot on how many members I manage to acquire. ",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
